    <item>
      <title>Ch.5 Superdense Coding</title>
      <link>https://dev-undergrad.dev/qiskit/05_superdense_coding/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:29:28 -0700</pubDate>
      <guid>https://dev-undergrad.dev/qiskit/05_superdense_coding/</guid>
      <description>$$ \sim * \backsim $$
Table of Contents § 13. Superdense Coding Protocol Analysis § 14. Qiskit Implementation Exercises Solutions $$ \backsim * \sim $$
In the last chapter, we studied the quantum teleportation protocol, which transmitted one qubit using two classical bits of communication, at the cost of one entangled e-bit.
The superdense coding protocol achieves the exact inverse. It allows for the transmission of two classical bits using on qubit of quantum information, at the cost of one e-bit.</description>
    </item>
